Prepare Android Studio migration: Fix XML headers

Android Studio will convert XML:
* Replace UTF-8 with utf-8 in the header
* Use double quotes instead of single ones in the header
* Remove the Byte Order Mark

Doing that in advance will allow Git to find back the files after they will
get moved in the new structure and preserve history.
